Jool is a gas giant planet with Laythe and two other small unnamed planets orbiting it.

As is logical, landing on a gas giant is impossible, but this doesn't prevent us from gathering resources from this giant.

§2Jool's atmosphere consists of §bHelium-3§r §2(25%), §bLiquid Hydrogen§r §2(25%), §bChlorine§r §2(20%), and §bNeon§r §2(12%). To collect all these gases, we will need a §3Harvester§r.§r
